junit.framework.Test
public class BasicJDBCTestCaseAdapter
extends junit.framework.TestCase

Delegator for JDBCTestModule. You can subclass this adapter or use JDBCTestModule directly (so your test case can use another base class). This basic adapter can be used if you don't need any other modules. It does not extend BaseTestCase. If you want to use several modules in conjunction, consider subclassing JDBCTestCaseAdapter. This class is generated from the JDBCTestModule and should not be edited directly.
